2. **Generate Mockups Using Stitch Prompts:**
   
   **Example for CNI Capture Screen (B02):**
   ```
   Create a mobile screen for CNI document capture with:
   - Full-screen camera view
   - Translucent dark overlay
   - Clear CNI-sized rectangle cutout in center (ID card proportions)
   - Animated orange corners (#E37B03) that pulse when aligned
